Hoërskool Kanonkop will host the first night race of the Middelburg Marathon Club’s Small 5 Night Race Series. The upcoming fun run, called Elephant Shrew, will be taking place at Hoërskool Kanonkop on February 23 from 19:00.The race consists of a 4.9km and 10km race. Prizes for the 10km men and ladies are as follows: R300 for first placeR200 for second placeR100 for third place Entry fees: Participants have the choice of either paying for a single entry or a discounted offer for all five races in the series:4.9km: R30 per single entry or R100 for all five races.10km: R80 per single entry or R300 for all five races. For more information, contact the Middelburg Marathon Club on 072 593 7346. The rest of the series will take place on the following dates: Buffalo Weaver: March 30Rhino Beetle: May 18Leopard Tortoise: September 21Ant Lion: November 23.